data.description: Discover the beauty of Kent Island living in this three bedroom, three bathroom water view home located at 132 Cecil Rd. Nestled on a peaceful Cul-de-sac, this home offers almost a full acre of privacy and nature with a detached one car garage and additional oversized storage shed. The exterior of the home offers multiple outdoor living spaces, from a screened in porch to a peaceful patio with built in fireplace and grill, and even a second floor deck off the primary suite with views of the Chesapeake Bay.   The interior of the home boasts three generously sized bedrooms, a beautifully updated kitchen with dining area, living room with vaulted ceilings, and even a separate room for laundry. Located just a short minute walk from the Romancoke pier; the perfect place for fishing, crabbing, and enjoying the Eastern Shore lifestyle. Home has public sewer and no HOA. Welcome home!
